\f0\fs24 \cf0 I'm building a personal Sleeper dynasty league analysis dashboard. I'm a total beginner at vibe coding \'97 I build the actual code in Claude Code, and I use this Project as a thinking and planning space.\
\
## My setup\
- Data source: Sleeper API (no auth needed, fully read-only)\
- Frontend: React (Vite) + Tailwind CSS\
- Storage: localStorage for caching API responses\
- Language: JavaScript\
\
## Vibe coding ground rules\
- One feature at a time, always in a working state\
- Before writing code, briefly explain what you're about to do and why\
- Simple and readable over clever\
- Name tradeoffs and recommend one approach\
- Explain decisions in plain language \'97 I'm learning\
\
