\
## Sleeper API \'97 complete endpoint reference\
\
### Two base URLs\
- Official documented endpoints: https://api.sleeper.app/v1/\
- Undocumented endpoints (stats, projections, schedule, depth chart): https://api.sleeper.com/\
  (no /v1/ prefix \'97 different base entirely)\
  Both .app and .com hostnames work on both sets of endpoints, but the convention above is what the community uses.\
\
### Rate limits & caching rules\
- Max 1000 API calls/minute or risk IP block\
- No authentication required\
- /v1/players/nfl is ~5MB \'97 cache in localStorage, call once per day max\
- Stats and projections responses are large \'97 always cache by week+season key\
- Undocumented endpoints (stats, projections, schedule, depth chart) are not officially supported.\
  They source data from Sportradar/Rotowire internally. They are stable and widely used but\
  could change without notice. Build with that in mind \'97 wrap them so they're easy to swap out.\
\
