\
### OFFICIAL ENDPOINTS (https://api.sleeper.app/v1/)\
\
#### User\
GET /v1/user/<username>\
GET /v1/user/<user_id>\
\uc0\u8594  returns: user_id, username, display_name, avatar\
\uc0\u8594  use for: entry point \'97 always store user_id (not username, which can change)\
\
#### Avatars\
Full: https://sleepercdn.com/avatars/<avatar_id>\
Thumb: https://sleepercdn.com/avatars/thumbs/<avatar_id>\
\uc0\u8594  use for: displaying manager/league avatars in the UI\
\
#### League\
GET /v1/user/<user_id>/leagues/nfl/<season>\
\uc0\u8594  returns: array of leagues with league_id, name, status (pre_draft/drafting/in_season/complete),\
  total_rosters, roster_positions, scoring_settings, season, previous_league_id, draft_id\
\uc0\u8594  use for: let user pick which league to analyze; read scoring format; chain seasons via previous_league_id\
\
GET /v1/league/<league_id>\
\uc0\u8594  returns: same as above but single league object\
\uc0\u8594  use for: confirm league config before loading everything else\
\
GET /v1/league/<league_id>/users\
\uc0\u8594  returns per manager: user_id, username, display_name, avatar, metadata.team_name, is_owner (commissioner flag)\
\uc0\u8594  use for: map roster_ids to real manager names and team names\
\
GET /v1/league/<league_id>/rosters\
\uc0\u8594  returns per team: roster_id, owner_id, players[] (full roster player_ids), starters[] (starting lineup player_ids),\
  reserve[] (IR), settings: \{ wins, losses, ties, fpts, fpts_decimal, fpts_against, fpts_against_decimal,\
  waiver_position, waiver_budget_used, total_moves \}\
\uc0\u8594  note: fpts/fpts_against are SEASON TOTALS (integer part only \'97 combine with fpts_decimal for full value)\
\uc0\u8594  bench = players[] minus starters[]\
\uc0\u8594  use for: current roster composition, season standings, total moves made, FAAB used\
\
GET /v1/league/<league_id>/matchups/<week>\
\uc0\u8594  returns per team: roster_id, matchup_id (same ID = opponents), points (float, weekly total),\
  custom_points (commissioner override, usually null), starters[], players[]\
\uc0\u8594  call for weeks 1\'9618 to build full season history\
\uc0\u8594  bench points = sum stats of (players minus starters) for that week\
\uc0\u8594  use for: week-by-week scores, expected wins calc, close game tracking, optimal lineup analysis\
\
GET /v1/league/<league_id>/winners_bracket\
GET /v1/league/<league_id>/losers_bracket\
\uc0\u8594  returns: array of matchup objects with fields:\
  r (round), m (matchup id), t1/t2 (roster_ids or \{w/l: matchup_id\}), w/l (winner/loser roster_id), p (final place)\
\uc0\u8594  note: official docs have a typo listing it as /loses_bracket \'97 correct path is /losers_bracket\
\uc0\u8594  use for: playoff history, final standings, championship results\
\
GET /v1/league/<league_id>/transactions/<week>\
\uc0\u8594  returns per transaction: type (trade / waiver / free_agent), status, roster_ids[],\
  adds \{player_id: roster_id\}, drops \{player_id: roster_id\},\
  draft_picks [\{season, round, roster_id (original), previous_owner_id, owner_id\}],\
  waiver_budget [\{sender, receiver, amount\}], creator (user_id), created (timestamp), leg (week)\
\uc0\u8594  for waiver types, settings may contain \{waiver_bid: amount\} for FAAB bids\
\uc0\u8594  call per week, chain across seasons via previous_league_id\
\uc0\u8594  use for: complete trade log, waiver activity, FAAB spend tracking, manager tendency analysis\
\
GET /v1/league/<league_id>/traded_picks\
\uc0\u8594  returns: all future picks that have been traded \'97 season, round, roster_id (original owner),\
  previous_owner_id, owner_id (current owner)\
\uc0\u8594  use for: who owns which future picks right now; draft capital tracker\
\
GET /v1/state/nfl\
\uc0\u8594  returns: week, season, season_type (pre/regular/post), season_start_date, previous_season,\
  leg (week of regular season), league_season, league_create_season, display_week\
\uc0\u8594  use for: know current week to cap matchup fetching; detect offseason vs in-season\
\
#### Drafts\
GET /v1/league/<league_id>/drafts\
\uc0\u8594  returns: array of all drafts \'97 type (snake/linear), status, season, settings (slots per position,\
  rounds, pick_timer), metadata (scoring_type, name), draft_id, league_id\
\uc0\u8594  dynasty leagues have one startup draft + one rookie draft per season\
\uc0\u8594  sorted most recent first\
\
GET /v1/draft/<draft_id>\
\uc0\u8594  returns: full draft object including draft_order \{user_id: slot\} and slot_to_roster_id \{slot: roster_id\}\
\uc0\u8594  use for: knowing who drafted in which slot\
\
GET /v1/draft/<draft_id>}